Author: lightandempty
Text: im at a family function for the weekend and it’s stressful bc im around my dad for most of the day and he makes me eat food. well, it’s more like i kind of have to eat regular meals bc he assumes i still eat like a normal person, lol. we went out for lunch yesterday with some other family and i was so nervous about eating as little as possible but not giving anything anyway about my ED.
